  }, "VAR Vetting: In-order to support the needs of confidential computing customers, value added resellers will need to undergo a vetting process prior to being provided some level of authorisation to produce solutions at particular levels for webizen-pro customers.  ", "These checks will include validation about personal background & professional skills.\xA0"), mdx("li", {
    parentName: "ol"
  }, "Webizen Agreement: The webizen agreement will cover various considerations; and will need to be held in \u2018good standing\u2019 in-order to maintain support arrangements.\xA0")), mdx("p", null, "Licensing Conditions will include a number of considerations; including but not limited to,"), mdx("ol", {
